---
title: Kiwi-Spiced Pork Meatballs with Charred Broccoli Salad & Mayonnaise
description: These pork meatballs have been mixed with our new favourite - Kiwi spice blend! Smokey flavours in tender pork mince are the
perfect complement to charred broccoli in a sweet and zingy dressing. Dig in!

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
